title: Prints
brief_description: Presents a number of simple printmaking processes, including found-object, vegetable and roller printing, string and cardboard printing and crayon graffito. Opens up a wide range of possibilities for individual exploration and experimentation. Suitable for upper primary and lower secondary levels.
